<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 01:52:36 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>酒店WiFi连接技巧</title><link>https://some.pics/69e829e0e99a1</link><description>&lt;p&gt;你难道不会在酒店时，通过手机网络更新iPadOS并下载浏览器，以便连接酒店的WiFi（然后连接VPN）吗？&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A laptop, an iPad and a TV. The laptop is downloading Firefox, the iPad is updating, and the TV is playing HGTV on a hotel room." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jasonm/69e829e0e99a1.jpg" width="5712"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jasonm.some.pics"&gt;@jasonm&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 01:52:36 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>自成一体</title><link>https://some.pics/69e7d6961dc83</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一个属于自己的世界。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Reflection of sky and chestnut tree in a streetside puddle. " height="4478" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/69e7d6961dc83.jpg" width="2522"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 19:57:13 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>探秘苔藓世界</title><link>https://some.pics/69e7c0f464254</link><description>&lt;p&gt;深入苔藓之中...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A flight of steps made of flat stone slabs leads through moss and trees to a clearing covered in moss. " height="2870" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/69e7c0f464254.jpg" width="2151"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 18:24:55 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>迪士尼旧照重现</title><link>https://some.pics/69e7b1eda63be</link><description>&lt;p&gt;开始扫描旧底片时，发现了这张2000年在华特迪士尼世界拍的照片。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&